title: Yamdena - Mark (Print)
description: Yamdena is an Austronesian language of Yamdena and surrounding islands in the Maluku Islands in Indonesia.

language.name: Yamdena
language.area: Southeast Maluku, east coast of Yamdena, north tip of Selaru, Adaut village; southwest Yamdena, Latdalam village. 35 villages.
